{"tid":1581321,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發] 《中英聯合聲明》並沒有條文訂下實行「雙普選」","createTime":"2019-09-19T13:37:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T23:31:45.000Z","uid":266844,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3d5bd2ed1f24c8d08fb1bac4f825ff19cccc366c","tid":1581321,"uid":266844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T13:37:57.000Z","msg":"對唔住，我係P牌，但我想講事實<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">[正視聽]<br />\n學生組織「學生動源」等專頁昨日在社交媒體，轉載今日下午沙田多家中學學生發起的人鏈活動宣傳時，提到「香港仍未實行雙普選，嚴重違反《中英聯合聲明》」。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">特區政府發言人今日下午發稿澄清，《中英聯合聲明》並沒有條文訂下實行「雙普選」</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n我有D野想講-<br />\n(1) <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府捉字蝨，愚弄市民</span></span><br />\n(2) 《中英聯合聲明》係冇寫「雙普選」，但係，中英聯合聲明嘅政策方針，係透過基本法去落實，所以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">違反基本法等於違反中英聯合聲明</span></span>。<br />\n(3) 而《基本法》<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第45條同第68條</span></span>清楚寫明<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">行政長官同立法會最終都係由普選產生 = 雙普選</span></span>。唔信的話自己睇。<br />\n(4) 既然係咁，主權移交咗成二十二年喇，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雙普選又冇，單普選又冇，plan又冇，時間表又冇，誠意又冇，咁樣條毛都冇</span></span>人地好難話政府[遵守]基本法個喎，咁唔遵守即係違反啦，咁「學生動源」係啱架喎!<br />\n(5) 政府發言人同梁振英，唔該<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好跳出嚟柒</span></span>啦，呢D事實係咁就咁，唔係你講就係!<br />\n<br />\n#中英聯合聲明<br />\n#基本法<br />\n#政府又呃人<br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/57vqZdQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F57vqZdQ.png&h=bfb2e13e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MTbaqTP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMTbaqTP.png&h=2173d0fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dgcEjdQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdgcEjdQ.png&h=68c7dcee&s={SIZE}\" /> 